Title: The US Soldier Facing Court-Martial
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbrwk
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
US soldier Joshua Key on facing a court-martial because he deserted rather than return to duty in Iraq. Also, the competitive French father who was jailed for manslaughter after slipping sedatives into the water bottles of their children's tennis opponents. Exposing family secrets. Finally, a Chinese version of 'Sex in the City' has been released. Show less